item.title: Ashmusy breaks down in tears as she responds to the people who accuse her of being a ‘runs girl’
item.description:
This was such an emotional interview.


Ashmusy has seen hell from the media and the comment section - they have questioned her talent, questioned her source of income, questioned her wealth, questioned her morals… and just thinking about all of the attacks she has had to endure, she broke down in tears on our set. 


She had to consciously change her dress sense, she tells me, because that was one of the reasons she was being stereotyped... Feed: https://feeds.acast.com/public/shows/611530cff76d810012d0f951

item.title: Behind The Mic: It Has To Be Me with Tess Masters
item.description: Are you ready to dive into the world of captivating storytelling and authentic connection? Look no further than Tess Masters, the host of the incredible podcast "It Has to Be Me." In this Behind-The-Mic interview, Tess shares her secrets to creating a podcast that truly resonates with listeners, from her meticulous preparation process to the power of intuition in the interview room...
